{"type": "article", "id": 28539, "title": "面包靠椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021714364oRsVGS60vDYX3hp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想坐在松松软软的面包上？日本书屋 Village Vanguard 最近就推出了几款以面包为设计灵感的靠椅，除了普通的白面包和烤面包造型之外，还有打上鸡蛋的吐司款和发霉的面包款，松松软软的看上去特别可爱。包括平放在地上用作坐垫，靠椅共有五个倾斜角度能够满足不同的需要，外套也可以拆卸下来进行清洗。脑洞大开的书屋或许是考虑到人们夏天会宅在空调房间里，还额外设计了煎蛋造型的大毯子和护膝毯，可以说是种草能力一流。这是它的<a href=\"http://vvstore.jp/feature/detail/8309/\">预定链接</a>，座椅的价格从 5378 到 7538 日元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171435pSuEOoIr45w86aPT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171435M9X4VDe1mqHTbGP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171435W8qvcyormY15GEbz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021714366ow7Q3uHEKVL9Rie.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}